cast.text:
Coming soon

We will be working with developers / projects that want to give users airdrops.

We’ll indicate what the developer is hoping to accomplish with the airdrop.

Users that 1) opt in 2) do the desired action—use a frame, engage in a channel, etc.—will start to develop reputation as a good user to offer future airdrops to.

Users that opt in, receive airdrops and don’t do the desired action will develop a reputation as a user to avoid offering airdrops. 

Ultimately, developers get to decide who to target (the data is permissionless). 

But I suspect airdrops on Farcaster will start to reward usage / go forward alignment.

First airdrop next week!
